usage:
  mllf dim [options] output_image
  required options:
  dim                             Image dimension (2 or 3)           
  -g atlas1.nii ....atlasN.nii    Warped atlas images
  -l label1.nii ....labelN.nii    Warped atlas segmentation
  -tg target.nii                  Target image
  -m [parameters]                 Isomap parameters K,dims
other options:
  -rp radius                      Patch radius (AxBxC)
  -rs radius                      Local search radius (AxBxC)
  -p  filenamePattern             Save the posterior maps,e.g. -p posterior%04d.nii.gz
  
